column5: Was to meet up with a member this morning up in Orrilla,but I broke a bolt on the header exhaust so had to stay local and have it looked at.Well since I had to wait til 10 for my machanic to arrive I figured I might as well fish K Bay. Head to my favorite hole and they were everywhere there.It was like looking in aqurium.Very cool.  Today every bait I threw,caught fish.  Im just going to leave you with pics.Action was fast and furious this morning.                         2morrow is the wifes day so no fishing.
What no pictures of the footware????
Nice fish. Sorry about the 1 none fishing day  . I wish I had some time to take off and do some fishing, 12.5hr days 5 days a week suck
Every bit you threw worked. That'd be nice. Is that a white goby bait you were using? Lunkerhunt? How did you rig it? Thanks.
Very nice Brian.  The white tubes work for smallies as well as lakers?
The white lure you see is a 2002 megabass. I bought it last year off of ebay.19 bucks plus shipping.It was used as well.  I try to only use it where I know there are no stealing toothy critters.
there are fish in kempenfelt bay??? geez I have to get out there someday
Yea,were so far from the water.LOL
sure go and post great fishing reports while I have to work...not nice at all   looks like I need to get out on simcoe soon
